original_title: Diamond Cobra vs the White Fox
overview: Based on two magical necklaces, both Tarjella and Diamond learn how jealousy and a evil curse can hurt the lives of family. The gangster squad and Rhonda are on the search for the white fox. Detective Parks and Agent Holly McCall are investigating these murders happening around the necklaces.
tagline: A sci-fi film you'll never forget!
title: Diamond Cobra vs the White Fox
